## Data Processing
This folder contains R scripts used for preprocessing and summarizing dual-seq transcriptome data.

## Input data
The following input files are required:
- "WGCNA_Readcount.csv" Expression counts generated from dual-seq transcriptomed.
- "Data_library_50.csv" Metadata describing the 50 sequencing libraries used in this study.

## Processing
The scripts in this folder perform the following steps:
- Generate expression profiles including:
  - TPM / coding length
  - TPM
  - log2(TPM+1)
- Produce distribution plots to visualize expression profiles across libraries
- Calculate correlations between all-genes based on their log2(TPM+1) values including:
  - interspecies correlations
  - intraspecies correlations

## The datasets generated here are used as input for downstream WGCNA analysis.
